Neuroconductor Packages

neuro_packages.Rd

Returns the vector of Neuroconductor packages

neuro_packages(...)

Arguments

...

Arguments passed to neuro_package_table

Value

vector of packages available on Neuroconductor

Examples

neuro_packages()
